asset.hookText:
KitchenAid® 12 inch Convection Bake Countertop Oven with full-size oven performance and fast results, convection bake and broil at temperatures up to 450 degrees (F) and 60 minute timer just like your full size oven, a warm function for reheating leftovers, a toast function for breads, bagels or sandwiches, and removable broil panwith grill and nonstick interior for easy cleaning.

Go to http://www.kitchenaid.com/countertop-appliances/ for more countertop appliance information and culinary inspiration.
